                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Franco-Italian Frontier</hi>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="italic">Rectification No. 4, Tenda and Briga district</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views the Council agreed to resume discussion of this
                    question at a later meeting.</p>
                <pb facs="0635" n="613" xml:id="pg_613"/>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Limitations on the Italian Navy</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After a discussion of the Naval Experts’ Report (<gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M.(46)</gloss> 121)<note n="7" xml:id="d199fn1">Dated June 22, 1946,
                            <ref target="#pg_584">p. 584</ref>.</note> no agreement was arrived
                    at.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Clauses Concerning the Danube</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Soviet Delegation tabled a proposal on the Danube (<gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M. (46)</gloss> 135).<note n="8" xml:id="d199fn2">Dated June 24, 1946,
                            <hi rend="italic">infra</hi>.</note> It was agreed to resume discussion
                    of this proposal at the Council’s next meeting.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">IV. <hi rend="italic">Personal Injuries</hi>
                </p>
                <p>(<hi rend="italic">Draft Peace Treaty with Roumania</hi> (<gloss target="#t_CFMD461">C.F.M.(D) (46)</gloss> 182. Art. 32)<note n="9" xml:id="d199fn3">Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <p>Art. 32 of the Draft Treaty with Roumania, dealing with personal injuries, was
                    deleted.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">V. <hi rend="italic">Mixed Arbitral Tribunals</hi>
                </p>
                <p>(<hi rend="italic">Draft Peace Treaty with Roumania</hi> (<gloss target="#t_CFMD461">C.F.M.(D) (46)</gloss> 182. Annex VI)<note n="9" xml:id="d199fn4">Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <p>It was agreed that this question should be considered by the Deputies at their
                    next meeting.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">VI. <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Council of Foreign Ministers, Tuesday, 25th June, at 4 p.m.</p>
